113","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 4B (§ 49 et seq.) of Title 29, Labor. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s49"},"text":"section 49 of Title 29","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id0dbb6965-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Carl D. Perkins Vocational and Applied Technology Education Act Amendments of 1990, and not as part of the Carl D. Perkins Career and Technical Education Act of 2006 which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s2303"},"text":"section 2303 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id0dbb6966-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Prior sections 2311 to 2313 were omitted in the general amendment of this chapter by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/332"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–332","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 2311, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/210/tI/s101"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–210, title I, § 101","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/524/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–524, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/2438"},"text":"98 Stat. 2438","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{